00:00:13,279 --> 00:00:16,079
actually the plan we had isn't the best, Ethan,

33
00:00:16,079 --> 00:00:18,760
we should change our plan to be this.

34
00:00:18,760 --> 00:00:20,719
I need someone who can carry that message

35
00:00:20,719 --> 00:00:23,440
and explain it to me in a way that I feel good about it.

36
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:27,280
Right, that I feel like, oh, okay, we learned something

37
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,839
and changing our plan is a good decision,

38
00:00:02,839 --> 00:00:06,500
as opposed to me thinking, for example, like, oh, maybe

