00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:09,519
Right?

41
00:00:09,519 --> 00:00:11,160
Yeah.

42
00:00:11,160 --> 00:00:17,039
And so when I'm deciding who to promote,

43
00:00:17,039 --> 00:00:19,960
I'm looking for those skills.

44
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:22,660
All of these skills have to do with not just building

45
00:00:22,660 --> 00:00:25,980
technology, but your ability to explain it, understand it

46
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
and context and influence others.

